---
<section class="py-24 bg-indigo-600 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Motifs décoratifs -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 30\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M1.22676 0C1.91374 0 2.45351 0.539773 2.45351 1.22676C2.45351 1.91374 1.91374 2.45351 1.22676 2.45351C0.539773 2.45351 0 1.91374 0 1.22676C0 0.539773 0.539773 0 1.22676 0Z\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\"%3E%3C/path%3E%3C/svg%3E')] opacity-10"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full mb-8">
        <span class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-indigo-700 rounded-full">
          Newsletter gratuite
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Ne manquez aucune actualité
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-indigo-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Recevez nos meilleurs conseils, guides et actualités sur la recharge électrique directement dans votre boîte mail.
      </p>

      <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input 
          type="email" 
          placeholder="Votre email professionnel" 
          class="flex-1 px-6 py-4 rounded-full text-gray-900 bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 shadow-lg"
          required
        />
        <button 
          type="submit"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-yellow-400 text-indigo-900 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
        >
          Je m'inscris
        </button>
      </form>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-indigo-200">
        Vous pourrez vous désinscrire à tout moment. Aucun spam, promis !
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>